{"tid":1390732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周五公僕集會 3公務員團體不滿促調查","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:39:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b56557d69f10978cea3516baf32807d2f8e263e5","tid":1390732,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"有公務員計劃於星期五晚上在中環遮打花園發起集會，再次促請港府回應五大訴求。<span style=\"color: red;\">政府人員協會、國家行政學院香港同學會，以及香港公務員總工會</span>，今日發表聯合聲明，批評他們公開發表政治言論，並發起政治集會行動，更有人在網絡上呼籲公務員罷工，明顯違反公務員守則，違背公務員誠信。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，公務員政治中立，支持特首領導特區政府依法施政，絕不認同這種企圖以少數人的立場，訛稱代表整個公務員隊伍的做法，又呼籲所有公務員勿受有心人誤導，促請公務員事務局及相關部門首長跟進調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2205522/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2205522%2F&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=f73428d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2205522/</a>"},{"pid":"baccefdc7814147be9a899cc68be84565ce01e84","tid":1390732,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"531e8a6625308f4de8a8f78d98fbbb68f7b86bb5","tid":1390732,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:16:41.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"a40fb30aab486865f4b456374fbcec08c418d18f","tid":1390732,"uid":245644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:18:12.000Z","msg":"香港公務員總工會？聽個名又係似無乜會員的扮大袋會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104b364ff5c41cb0e377a94c2d4052b6c64b6243","tid":1390732,"uid":39796,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"公務員政治中立<br />\n支持特首領導特區政府依法施政<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed76374b2acd2782ce433711b7e8d14e9a769897","tid":1390732,"uid":169074,"like":4,"di